name: Gazer Shark
effectText: You can banish this card from your GY, then target 2 Level 5 WATER monsters in your GY, except "Gazer Shark"; Special Summon both those monsters, but their effects are negated. Immediately after this effect resolves, Xyz Summon 1 WATER monster using only those 2 monsters. You can only use this effect of "Gazer Shark" once per turn.
